{"word":"διακωλύω","slug":"διακωλύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διακωλύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ύσω</el>) </el><p/><i>to hinder, prevent</i>, <el>τινὰ μὴ ποιεῖν τι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; or without <el>μή</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a>;</b> <el>δ. τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a>;</b> <el>δ. φόνον</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἃ διεκωλύθη</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>ποιεῖν</el>) which <i>he was prevented</i> from doing, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}